Too good music composition - which we used to hear in karawara/goa.
Kannada - ensemble of languages - branches as konkani and then to marathi and gujarati.
Words which are same in present Kannada:
Khalasi - Kalasi - a seaman / military worker ( kalasipalya - a place in Bengalur )
Vavata - from Bavuta ( flag )
